Text: Introduction For Our MeetingIm Maurice Nunas the recently hired Director of Government Affairs in Singapore working for Sue Nord Sue has arranged an introductory meeti ng with you next week Week of July In preparation for that meeting I attach for your information a brief description of my particulars and background Bio Maurice Nunasdoc As I am new to EBS and to Enron I would like to learn as much as possible from you If you have anything you would like me to read before our mee ting please send it to me by email before Friday morning thanks I look forward to our meeting Best regards Maurice
